{"tid":630782,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺依加香港音樂電影頒獎都係有「佢未攞過俾佢攞」的感覺","createTime":"2018-04-16T01:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T15:30:25.000Z","uid":127972,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"de1ffd39654c0b5a8cad41d88e3ebcbe0fd8dd92","tid":630782,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"冇錯，得獎者係有料<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解近年的頒獎禮總有變相做鼓勵獎、安慰獎、年資獎的感覺<br />\n<br />\n當年張敬軒903金獎，個感覺係「努力咁多年，俾佢攞啦」（當然可以係對手不滯）<br />\n今年古天樂又有咁的感覺<br />\n唔係話得獎人唔好，而係按作品去頒<br />\n<br />\n其實凌志龍有力問鼎男主角，我會覺得頒俾個有料的新人好過輪資排輩。<br />\n<br />\n利申：非專業，只係講出感覺"},{"pid":"d05026c1b13756a5ce91460dcbae7b120349a914","tid":630782,"uid":127972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd5cd51e30f1480996043b069b9fb45d55f904f","tid":630782,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67e387cda91df31d9dfc77ce514df53565705ee","tid":630782,"uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"有啲保留，無錯呢啲獎睇上來好似係排隊獎，排得越耐就越有機攞，但係轉返轉諗，太早攞又會唔會係好事？<br />\n袁詠儀、張柏芝都係短時間內攞到最佳女主角，但之後無以為繼。"},{"pid":"af8f51e4429b5806e54cfc54442cfe06c26bb68c","tid":630782,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"舊年其實余文樂較好"},{"pid":"cc9f14ead56ae7d52cdfa67b2ff18b6f9a5cf689","tid":630782,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"仲有黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e48de021050d4524d8dba0826e2d44924ea05","tid":630782,"uid":89608,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"小圈子選舉, 全部都係圍爐取暖獎, 拎左都冇乜意思"},{"pid":"c4ccd60a57b9a19f4e0ffaa2dfff0af11c0c8427","tid":630782,"